settings.para: The National Down Syndrome Society (NDSS) and behno collaborate to create a significant partnership to further behno’s commitment to being a wholesome social enterprise founded on championing ethical manufacturing to now supporting nonprofits working to positively impact their communities.

settings.secHeading: The National Down Syndrome Society x behno.
settings.afterImageText: WITHIN THE CAPSULE COLLECTION ARE OUR SIGNATURE BAGS, ALL IN RED TO HONOR NDSS’ OFFICIAL COLOR. 20% OF ALL SALES ARE DONATED TO NDSS.
